@startuml
participant "User Code" as User
participant "Hook (sleep)" as Hook
participant "IOManager" as IOM
participant "Current Fiber" as Fib
participant "Scheduler (MainLoop)" as Sched

User -> Hook: sleep(1)
activate Hook

Hook -> IOM: addTimer(1000ms, schedule_callback)
note right: 注册1秒后的回调：\n把当前协程重新加入调度队列

Hook -> Fib: YieldToHold()
activate Fib
Fib -> Sched: swapOut() (切换上下文)
deactivate Fib
note right: **关键点**：\n保存当前栈，切换回调度线程栈

activate Sched
Sched -> IOM: idle() (进入epoll_wait)
note right: 线程阻塞等待IO或定时器
... 1秒后 ...
IOM -> Sched: 定时器超时，触发回调
Sched -> Sched: schedule(Fib)
note right: 协程重回就绪队列

Sched -> Fib: swapIn() (恢复上下文)
deactivate Sched
activate Fib

Fib -> Hook: return from Yield
deactivate Fib

Hook -> User: return 0
deactivate Hook
@enduml
